## What Business Problems Did This Dashboard Solve? 

1 Free users churn at 12% (vs 6% for paid). This Signals a strong opportunity to improve onboarding and increase conversions.

2. Micro-subscription plans can unlock a new paying segment. This helps reduce price-barrier drop-offs for students/job seekers.

3. A/B testing on pricing & course recommendations is essential. Can increase conversion probability and boost LTV.

4.  Badges & explore more options with personalized recommendations can sustain engagement. Reduces early-stage churn and strengthens retention.

5. A free Prompt Engineering mini-course can attract high-intent learners. Supports AI learning adoption while reducing chatbot costs.

## Overall Business Impact of the Insights

Through this analysis, the platform can:
✔ Reduce churn by addressing user motivations early
✔ Improve conversion through targeted pricing and content strategies
✔ Increase retention through engagement-focused features
✔ Strengthen the learning funnel from free → premium users
✔ Drive predictable and scalable revenue growth
